## The Autonomous QA Loop

If any issue happen, you must autonomously debug it. Use help from the produced log file, screenshot and all ur tools to help yourself (web search, context7, code execution ...) and then re-run the application with the sh script. 


Absolute constraints : Do not test the camera live in this mode (the live scanner) as it cause trouble with permissions. 